      children: "A photo illustration showing several people in silhouette with a big Google logo behind them. Google is among many companies that have been developing and testing a new type of chatbot that can riff on almost any topic thrown its way.Credit...Kenzo Tribouillard/Agence France-Presse — Getty Images"
