    }), _jsx(_components.p, {
      children: "I fill out the journal every day Consistency is key. It felt great to complete the first journal by hand. I might buy it again. There is something very satisfying about opening the journal in your hands and looking back at six months of pages full of transformational gratitude, optimism and affirmations turned into reality. For now, I've been using the PyFiveMinuteJournal Python application."
    }), _jsx(_components.p, {
