    }), _jsx(_components.p, {
      children: "I highly recommend it If you are a developer, you can clone the PyFiveMinuteJournal from the GitHub repository and start journaling on your computer. If you are not into command-line applications or you prefer writing by hand, then order The Five Minute Journal from Intelligent Change. It might change your life."
    }), _jsx(_components.p, {
